This reproducibility report provides details about the artifact evaluation done with regards to the Artifact Description and Evaluation appendix of SC25 paper MetoHash: A Memory-Efficient and Traffic-Optimized Hashing Index on Hybrid PMem-DRAM Memories by Xiaoli Wang, Ronglong Wu, Zixiang Yu, Zhirong Shen, Zhifeng Bao, Chuanhui Yang, Guangyang Deng, Quanqing Xu, and Qiangsheng Su. The work was done as part of the Reproducibility Initiative of SC25. The author is a member of the SC25 Reproducibility Committee.